text: Very pleased with the bank officer/teller Ms Toh who attended to me today. She was very patient, helpful and courteous. 5 stars for her!!
Excellent service of staff-Eleanor. Good job and well done. Thank you.
The most friendly and efficient Maybank branch that i have ever been to. Staff are so courteous and professional in handling  issues. Everything is a breeze.
Had a very pleasant experience at this branch. Counter staff were very patient and helpful. There is a wait time but it's processed very orderly. Staff try to do their best to accommodate your needs.
Great service from all the staffs! Thank you to these kind and patient staffs for accommodating to me!
